(above), who wound up with three touchdown catches. JAYNE KAMIN-ONCEA / Los 
Angeles Times; Photo, At left, Montana scrambles for yardage in the first 
quarter, Reuters; Photo, and, at right, he celebrates a touchdown pass to Rice 
in the second quarter. JAYNE KAMIN-ONCEA / Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</GRAPHIC>
