</P>
</TYPE>
<SUBJECT>
<P>
SUPER BOWL (FOOTBALL GAME); FOOTBALL CHAMPIONSHIPS; SAN FRANCISCO 49ERS 
(FOOTBALL TEAM); DENVER BRONCOS (FOOTBALL TEAM); ELWAY, JOHN 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA012990-0071 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 168703 </DOCID>
<DATE>
<P>
January 29, 1990, Monday, Home Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Sports; Part C; Page 4; Column 1; Sports Desk 
</P>
</SECTION>
