<HEADLINE>
<P>
NEWSWIRE 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Linford Christie of England won the 100 meters in a wind-aided 9.93 seconds in 
the Commonwealth Games at Auckland, New Zealand, one-hundredth of a second off 
Carl Lewis' world record. 
</P>
<P>
