viewing is to Spanish-language television. Therefore, 50% of 10% will be 5%. So 
we believe we are getting 5% of the viewing and 1% of the advertiser revenue." 
-- J. William Grimes, president of Univision Holdings, owner of KMEX Channel 34 
and other Spanish-language stations, in Electronic Media 
</P>
