<SUBJECT>
<P>
POLITICAL ADVERTISING; POLITICAL CANDIDATES; WIEDER, HARRIETT M; KASHI CO; 
SNACK FOODS; ORANGE COUNTY -- GOVERNMENT OFFICIALS; ORANGE COUNTY -- ELECTIONS 
-- 1990 
